Revision history for Module::Build::DistVersion

0.03   April 25, 2008
	- Don't require =head1 VERSION if a module has no POD

0.02   April 25, 2008
	- Added optional changes=N argument
	- Don't index the tools directory
	- Note that subclasses should "use Module::Build"
	  before trying to load Module::Build::DistVersion

0.01   April 15, 2008
	- Initial release

0.00   February 29, 2008
	- Module created
